

  <header class="sticky top-0 z-50 bg-white/95 backdrop-blur-xl border-b px-6 py-4 flex items-center justify-between">
    <a href="index.html" class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-[0.12em] text-black no-underline section-title">EL-<span class="font-light text-neutral-700 text-lg">ATTIRE</span></a>
    <a href="index.html" class="text-sm text-neutral-500 hover:text-black"><i class="fas fa-arrow-left mr-1"></i> Back to Store</a>
  </header>

  <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-10 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-light section-title mb-2">Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
    <p class="text-neutral-500 mb-8">Find answers to common questions about our tailoring services, fabrics, orders, and more.</p>

    <!-- Search -->
    <div class="search-box mb-10">
      <input type="text" id="faqSearch" placeholder="Search questions...">
      <i class="fas fa-search"></i>
    </div>

    <!-- Categories -->
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 mb-10">
      <button class="category-btn active-cat" data-cat="all">All</button>
      <button class="category-btn" data-cat="tailoring">Tailoring</button>
      <button class="category-btn" data-cat="orders">Orders & Payments</button>
      <button class="category-btn" data-cat="shipping">Shipping & Delivery</button>
      <button class="category-btn" data-cat="measurements">Measurements</button>
      <button class="category-btn" data-cat="fabrics">Fabrics</button>
      <button class="category-btn" data-cat="account">Account</button>
    </div>

    <!-- FAQ List -->
    <div id="faqList">
      <div class="faq-item" data-cat="tailoring">
        <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">How long does bespoke tailoring take? <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i></div>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>Bespoke tailoring typically takes 10-21 business days depending on the complexity of the garment and current workload. Premium and Concierge tier orders receive priority processing. You'll receive a detailed timeline during your consultation.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item" data-cat="tailoring">
        <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">Can I make changes after placing a tailoring order? <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i></div>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>Minor adjustments can be made within 48 hours of placing your order. Significant design changes after production has begun may incur additional costs and extend the delivery timeline. Contact your tailor immediately if you need to make changes.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item" data-cat="measurements">
        <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">How do I provide my measurements? <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i></div>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>You can provide measurements in three ways: 1) Visit our Lagos or Abuja studio for professional in-person measurement, 2) Schedule a virtual consultation where we guide you through the process, or 3) Enter your measurements manually in your account profile using our interactive measurement guide.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item" data-cat="measurements">
        <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">What if my measurements are incorrect? <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i></div>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>We strongly recommend professional measurement for the best fit. If you provide self-measurements that result in an ill-fitting garment, we offer one complimentary adjustment. Additional alterations may be charged. Our master tailors review all measurements before production begins.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item" data-cat="orders">
        <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">What payment methods do you accept? <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i></div>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>We accept all major credit and debit cards (Visa, Mastercard, American Express), bank transfers, and mobile money payments. For bespoke orders over $500, a 50% deposit is required to begin work, with the balance due upon completion.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item" data-cat="orders">
        <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">Can I cancel my order? <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i></div>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>Ready-to-wear orders can be cancelled within 24 hours for a full refund. Bespoke tailoring orders: deposits are non-refundable once production has begun. Contact our support team immediately if you need to cancel.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item" data-cat="shipping">
        <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">Do you ship internationally? <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i></div>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>Yes! We ship to over 30 countries worldwide. International shipping rates are calculated at checkout based on destination and package weight. Please note that customers are responsible for any customs duties, taxes, or import fees imposed by their country.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item" data-cat="shipping">
        <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">How can I track my order? <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i></div>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>Once your order ships, you'll receive an email with a tracking number. You can also track your order status in real-time from your account dashboard under "My Orders." For tailoring orders, you can monitor progress through each stage of production.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item" data-cat="fabrics">
        <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">Can I request fabric samples? <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i></div>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>Absolutely! We offer complimentary fabric swatches for most of our collection. You can request up to 5 swatches per order through our fabric page. Swatches typically arrive within 5-7 business days. This helps you feel the texture and see the true color before committing.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item" data-cat="fabrics">
        <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">Where do your fabrics come from? <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i></div>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>Our fabrics are sourced from premium suppliers in Nigeria (Aso Oke, Adire), Italy (damask, silk), Turkey (cotton blends), and India (brocade, embroidery). We personally vet all suppliers to ensure quality, ethical production, and authentic materials.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item" data-cat="account">
        <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">How do I create an account? <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i></div>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>Creating an account is simple and free. Click "Sign In" on the top menu, then select "Create Account." You'll need your phone number (which serves as your username), email address, and a password. Once registered, you can save measurements, track orders, and manage your profile.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item" data-cat="tailoring">
        <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">What's the difference between your service tiers? <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i></div>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p><strong>Essential ($95):</strong> Standard measurement, basic fabric selection, 1 fitting, 2-week turnaround.<br><strong>Premium ($195):</strong> Precision measurement, premium fabric consultation, 2 fittings, 10-day turnaround, embroidery options.<br><strong>Concierge ($495):</strong> Home visit measurement, exclusive fabric sourcing, unlimited fittings, 5-day priority turnaround, custom embroidery & beading, personal stylist.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- No results -->
    <div id="noResults" class="hidden text-center py-12">
      <i class="fas fa-search text-4xl text-neutral-300 mb-4"></i>
      <p class="text-neutral-500">No questions found matching your search.</p>
      <p class="text-sm text-neutral-400 mt-1">Try different keywords or browse all categories.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Contact CTA -->
    <div class="mt-16 p-8 bg-neutral-50 rounded-lg text-center">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-light section-title mb-2">Still have questions?</h3>
      <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 mb-4">Our support team is ready to help you.</p>
      <div class="flex gap-4 justify-center flex-wrap">
        <a href="mailto:support@elattire.com" class="btn-black px-8 py-3 uppercase text-xs inline-block no-underline"><i class="fas fa-envelope mr-2"></i> Email Us</a>
        <a href="tel:+2341234567" class="btn-outline px-8 py-3 uppercase text-xs inline-block no-underline"><i class="fas fa-phone mr-2"></i> Call Us</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <footer class="bg-[#0a0a0a] text-neutral-400 px-6 md:px-10 py-12 text-center text-xs">
    <p>EL-ATTIRE · Bespoke Nigerian Tailoring · Lagos | Abuja | Milano</p>
  </footer>

  <script>
    (function() {
      // Toggle FAQ items
      window.toggleFaq = function(question) {
        const item = question.parentElement;
        const isOpen = item.classList.contains('open');
        // Close all
        document.querySelectorAll('.faq-item').forEach(i => i.classList.remove('open'));
        // Open clicked if it wasn't open
        if (!isOpen) item.classList.add('open');
      };

      // Category filtering
      const categoryBtns = document.querySelectorAll('.category-btn');
      categoryBtns.forEach(btn => {
        btn.addEventListener('click', function() {
          categoryBtns.forEach(b => b.classList.remove('active-cat'));
          this.classList.add('active-cat');
          const cat = this.dataset.cat;
          filterFAQs(cat, document.getElementById('faqSearch').value);
        });
      });

      // Search
      document.getElementById('faqSearch').addEventListener('input', function() {
        const activeCat = document.querySelector('.category-btn.active-cat')?.dataset.cat || 'all';
        filterFAQs(activeCat, this.value);
      });

      function filterFAQs(category, searchTerm) {
        const items = document.querySelectorAll('.faq-item');
        let visibleCount = 0;
        
        items.forEach(item => {
          const cat = item.dataset.cat;
          const text = item.textContent.toLowerCase();
          const matchesCat = category === 'all' || cat === category;
          const matchesSearch = !searchTerm || text.includes(searchTerm.toLowerCase());
          
          if (matchesCat && matchesSearch) {
            item.style.display = 'block';
            visibleCount++;
          } else {
            item.style.display = 'none';
          }
        });

        document.getElementById('noResults').classList.toggle('hidden', visibleCount > 0);
      }
    })();
  </script>
